THR Liberal Activists framing Charlie Kirk's assassination as deserved

Charlie Kirk is a conservative activist and has campaigned against liberal ideas suck as affirmative actin, progressive taxation, climate change policies and diversity programs in universities. He frames these as threats to free markets and traditional values, positioning his activism as a pushback against what he calls "lesftist indoctrination" on campuses.

This house believes that it is in the interest of gaming companies (e.g:-SONY, Nintendo) to aggressively crack down (e.g:- sue individual fans, force websites to take it down) on the creation and consumption of ROM hacks

ROM hacking is the process of modifying a video game to alter the game's graphics,dialogue, levels, gameplay, and/or other elements. In series like Pokémon, ROM hacks exist as fan-made games that elevate the enjoyability of existing gaming experiences. Creating ROM hacks often violate many IP laws

This house would remove all statutes of limitations.

The statute of limitations sets a time limit for filing lawsuits. For crimes with this limit,prosecution is barred after the period ends. e.g. In India, the statute of limitations for theft is 3 years. The time limit varies for different types of crimes and offenses, but usually only some major, grave crimes (e.g. war crime, murder etc) do not have a statute of limitation
THBT it is in the interest of the Sri Lankan govt to restrict tourism and trade with Israel

This house prefers a world where there is a predominant belief that the "currency of life is time"

Currency of life is time" is the belief that the value of material wealth and money diminishes with age since your time and ability to use it decreases. Rather than the pursuit of increasing material wealth, it promotes maximizing happiness. For instance, a 40 year old man with 3 million dollars is considered richer than a 80 year old man with 6 million dollars

This house,as the daughter, would enter into a relationship with Batman

You are the daughter of a rich & famous criminal( Eg:- Carmine Falcone) in the city of Gotham. Despite the chaos and danger of your upbringing, your heart has found its anchor in Batman. Over the past months, your encounters with him have grown deeper, moving beyond fleeting romance into something profound and irreplaceable. He is not just a source of catharsis but the one person who truly understands you.

THP feminism that encourages disengagement from patriarchal structures (e.g:- marriage, having children) over feminism that seeks to reform them from within ( Advocating for equal responsibilities in marriage, greater maternal benefits)

This house would implement one year of mandatory national service for young people (Eg:-In countries such as South Korea, Israel and Norway, men and women must serve in sectors that include but are not limited to the infantry, engineering and logistics, community services like libraries and local councils)

TH, as the Debater, would quit Debating.

You are a Debater in the Local Debating Circuit, and have been debating since you were 13 years old. Your career started off slow but in the past year you and your team members have achieved immense success individually, ranking amongst the Top 10 Speakers consistently. You and your teammates are extremely close and have longed and dreamed to win a championship together. Unfortunately, even with your individual success you and your teammates still haven't been able to win a championship yet, coming close multiple times. Seperately you also have the dream of getting into a prestigious local University and have your ALs coming up in about an year's time so finding a balance between both is becoming increasingly difficult.
